imdb.plot outline: The world is full of terrible things. War. Famine. Slavery. This show discusses the terrible things that truly matter to Americans: pop-culture and strange human behaviors. The nonsense things we do will surely end up burning in hell. Hosted by comedian Phoenix West.
imdb.title: Things That Will Burn in Hell with Phoenix West
akas: Things That Will Burn in Hell with Phoenix West (United States)
plot: Humans truly hate themselves. We do weird things without thinking why. This show breaks those things down. Hosted by Phoenix West.::Loitering In Wonderland Studios
